{"tid":271189,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【倫敦橋連環襲】一兇徒穿阿仙奴球衣行兇 傳巴基斯坦出生","createTime":"2017-06-05T01:15:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T05:56:45.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb1920a54755c4721873dc39d737d44ee3ada515","tid":271189,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170605/large/1496616753_3792.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170605%2Flarge%2F1496616753_3792.jpg&h=c7201831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦橋連環恐襲，警方並未公佈行兇者身份，但英國傳媒報道，其中一名兇徒已為人父，表面是好好先生，實際卻仇恨西方價值。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒拍到三名兇徒在倫敦橋開車撞人後，下車在酒吧區博羅市場（Borough Market）步行，準備再開殺戒的一刻。片段見到其中一名兇徒穿英超球隊阿仙奴藍色球衣。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》報道，該名穿球衣的兇徒在巴基斯坦出生，育有至少兩孩，住在倫敦東郊巴金（Barking）。居民說他表面是好好先生，經常與鄰居小孩打乒乓球和踢足球，很得鄰居信賴，讓孩子與他獨處也不怕。不過，他據說心中卻仇恨西方價值，最近經常改變打扮。"},{"pid":"f2ce3eb621b7c60bddb5cadf101b7af59df0dbc7","tid":271189,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"阿狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae99201ec98dd751485aa82286954c846a3bee4","tid":271189,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:21:05.000Z","msg":"主腦係雲x?"},{"pid":"8ae7b1493643dc400bb16a67ccb7f5954796f43b","tid":271189,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T02:24:54.000Z","msg":"宣洩對永續雲爺爺既不滿？"},{"pid":"0a73001e1af66631826c3b60d48f47c34a753567","tid":271189,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislik